    {
      "title": "Set up",
      "content": "Two pieces sum to 96: x + y = 96. The longer piece is 6 more than 4 times the shorter: x = 4y + 6."
    },
    {
      "title": "Solve",
      "content": "Substitute: (4y + 6) + y = 96 $\\Rightarrow$ 5y = 90 $\\Rightarrow$ y = 18. Then x = 4(18) + 6 = 78."
    },
    {
      "title": "Answer",
      "content": "x = 78, which confirms <strong>D</strong> &mdash; <strong>D</strong> is correct."
    }
